This repository is an artifact for the ISPASS 2026 paper
"GTPin: Enhancing Intel GPU Profiling With High-Level Binary Instrumentation".

It bundles several third-party components, each under its own license.
The license that applies to each file is determined by the component it belongs
to, as described below.

